creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the official Vineyard Christian Church app!

Find out more about our church, listen to sermons, get information about upcoming events, and more!

Here are some of the things you can do with our app:
Fill out a Connect Card during one of our services
Get directions to our church using your phone's navigation system
Watch sermons you've missed
Read that Sunday's Scripture passage
See all of our Connect Groups and pick a group to visit
Learn about the different ministries in our church
Look for upcoming events and register for them
Share about our church on social media
Access leader resources
Give online or through the app

Sunday Services: 9 AM & 10:30 AM

For more information about Vineyard Christian Church, please visit:
http://www.vineyard-christian.org/

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes new features, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
New:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
Improved:
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
Fixed:
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.
